      "post_content": "Interesting, [Reckless Spite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reckless Spite) is an **instant** but **destroys** two **nonblack** creatures. Not sure which one is better.\n  \nNonartifact > Nonblack (I think). Exile > Destroy. Sorcery < Instant.\n  \n   \nIt will not work for [Darksteel Colossus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darksteel Colossus) because it's an artifact.",
